{"tid":498517,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[CCTVB不敢報排華]大冬天就停電停水，給老百姓、給打工的，真的不當作人。","createTime":"2017-12-14T01:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T00:21:14.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb89817a1891504e9a43f28ca7f2ee6bff211d2","tid":498517,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:00:27.000Z","msg":"有線中國組<br />\n10 hrs &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【這邊廂，蔡奇說要安排好外省勞工的食宿生活】<br />\n【那邊廂，北京繼續斷水斷電驅逐外來人口】<br />\n<br />\n北京大興區舊宮鎮在周日示威後，仍然繼續停水停電趕人走，有外來工人為等發薪金，無奈要在斷水斷電的出租屋，摸黑捱凍生活。<br />\n<br />\n來了北京十多年的王先生，原本是建築工人，想掙錢寄回老家，但現在在北京生活愈來愈難，他說決定稍後就會回老家，以後都不再回北京：「大冬天就停電停水，給老百姓、給打工的，真的不當作人。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1583183665159447/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1583183665159447%2F&d=yokb69uU2TaPlFT3jV6eCxxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=3717b8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1583183665159447/</a>"},{"pid":"40eeab070ca17a6a56c3d2809bca1fe3f792f4fe","tid":498517,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"垃圾tvb"},{"pid":"a646e2cd589e9bc40837e0bd0c80851352346e4a","tid":498517,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢報既話就天開眼"},{"pid":"22696bb2526f837ba4b9fed26ea6c609f881525f","tid":498517,"uid":34666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:07:43.000Z","msg":"停電停水咪係黨既安排囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca24ce2ba76dc9ff4486ae15e341899b008456e","tid":498517,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"仲狙擊緊日本工業醜閒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ac73a8599a9457a30b73328753d78d190f0dc7","tid":498517,"uid":51717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit